import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import AppContext from './AppContext'

ReactDOM.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
        <AppContext.Provider value={{loaded: false}}>
           <App />
        </AppContext.Provider >
    </React.StrictMode>,
    document.getElementById('root')
)
